longBusinessSummary: Kerevitas Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and trades in frozen and canned products in Turkey. The company offers frozen bakery products, vegetables and fruit products, potatoes and croquettes, meat products, and sea food; canned tuna, vegetables, and convenience foods; and consumer margarine, out-of-home consumption, and cooking oil products. The company was founded in 1970 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Kerevitas Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Yildiz Holding A.S.
